# Task Management App

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-Ready-2496ED?logo=docker&logoColor=white)](#docker)
[![Laravel](https://img.shields.io/badge/Laravel-10.x-FF2D20?logo=laravel&logoColor=white)](#tech-stack)
[![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-18.x-61DAFB?logo=react&logoColor=black)](#tech-stack)
[![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/TypeScript-5.x-3178C6?logo=typescript&logoColor=white)](#tech-stack)

A modern, full-stack Task Management application built with Laravel API backend and React + TypeScript frontend. Features JWT authentication, task CRUD operations, and a responsive UI.

![Task Management App Preview](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400.png?text=Task+Management+App+Screenshot)

## ‚ú® Features

### üîê Authentication & Security
- User registration & login with JWT tokens
- Laravel Sanctum for API authentication
- Protected routes and API endpoints
- Secure password hashing

### üìù Task Management
- Create, Read, Update, Delete tasks
- Task status tracking: `pending`, `in_progress`, `done`
- User-scoped tasks (users only see their own tasks)
- Paginated task list (10 tasks per page)
- Search and filter functionality

### üé® Frontend
- Modern React 18 with TypeScript
- Vite for fast development and building
- Tailwind CSS for responsive design
- Hot reload for rapid development
- Clean, intuitive user interface

### üê≥ Development & Deployment
- Docker Compose setup for easy local development
- SQLite for development, MySQL for production
- Environment-based configuration
- Comprehensive API documentation

## üõ† Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Laravel 10.x** - PHP framework
- **Laravel Sanctum** - API authentication
- **SQLite** - Development database
- **MySQL** - Production database (optional)

### Frontend
- **React 18** - UI library
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
- **Vite** - Build tool and dev server
- **Tailwind CSS** - Styling
- **Axios** - HTTP client
- **React Router** - Navigation
- **React Hot Toast** - Notifications

### DevOps & Tools
- **Docker & Docker Compose** - Containerization
- **Git** - Version control
- **Postman/Insomnia** - API testing

## üöÄ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Docker & Docker Compose (recommended)
- *OR* PHP 8.1+, Composer, Node.js 18+, npm

### Using Docker (Recommended)

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/ayaos123/task-management-app.git
   cd task-management-app
